            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Pick one. Say it three times in the morning, hand on chest. Move to a different one tomorrow if the first one doesn't fit. None of them require you to believe they're true yet, saying them is the first step toward that.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
